{"tid":1631813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和勇同心 長期抗爭","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:23.000Z","uid":77752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4346b0ab2878c56dc4450471ae3a523327a1058","tid":1631813,"uid":77752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:20:31.000Z","msg":"呢幾日發生好多事，有好多矛盾，連連登都有唔少分化撚出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係想同各位講句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>勿忘初心!!</strong></span><br />\n有啲嬌情，但我覺得亂到唔知做咩嘅時候 <br />\n最好諗翻當初大家都係為左捍衛自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好俾五毛影響到!<br />\n有咩做得唔好都一齊改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足一條心，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">打倒共匪!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，加油!</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人，反抗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1827f09605a5f3193b81c9057936abbdf7cd0504","tid":1631813,"uid":77752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f752140f058ca53c5fa2893458b41523a88fc7","tid":1631813,"uid":77752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:16.000Z","msg":"唔好氣餒呀!!!!"},{"pid":"26541b0af849566d2d5c12f930b995c52fdb7d37","tid":1631813,"uid":77752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}